name: Battlewasp - Nest
desc: When your "Battlewasp" monster is targeted for an attack: You can Special Summon 1 "Battlewasp" monster from your hand or Deck, and if you do, place 1 counter on this card, then end the Battle Phase. You can only use this effect of "Battlewasp - Nest" once per turn. During the End Phase, send this card with 2 or more counters to the GY.
str1: Do you want to use the effect?
